info.name: Good Morning [Tumblr post icons]
info.description: Tumblr 'new post' icons for your dashboard. "In English, 'good morning' is a typical greeting. Its literal French translation, 'bon matin,' is not. If you want to greet someone in the morning, you just say bonjour. The only time you would use bon matin is in the expression de bon matin, which means 'bright and early.' " *
